/// 名称: MI.MIFI3000
/// 描述: 深圳亚辉龙iFlash3000 双向仪器接口
MIFI3000(mi)   
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
    s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12)      //项目分隔符
    s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13)  //结果分隔符
    s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14)        //抗生素分隔符
    s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15)        //药敏结果分隔符
    s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)   //端口号
    S mi1=mi
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
    F {
        D Main
        Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
    }
    C par4
    Q
  
Main
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC="" 
    R *R:10
    Q:'$TEST    //如果超时则退出
    Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
    S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
    K PLIST
    S index=1
    F {
        S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
        Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
        Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
        R *R:10
        Q:'$TEST    //如果超时则退出
        I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
            S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
            S PLIST(index)=""
        }
        I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
            S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
        }
        I $C(R)=cr {    //解析一条记录
            D Record
            K PLIST
            S index=1   
        }   
        Q:$C(R)=eb      //循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
    }
    D Save
    Q
  
Record
	K ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi)
    S index=""
    S segmentType="",dataTye="",graphType=""
    S isImage=0,isBinary=0
    F {
        S index=$O(PLIST(index))
        Q:'$L(index)
        S record=$TR($G(PLIST(index)),cr)
        Continue:'$L(record)
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
        I index=1 {
            S segmentType=$P(record,"|",1)
          ;消息段(数据类型) 	MSH	  MSA 	PID   OBR  	OBX  ORD  QRF 	ERR   QAK    DSP     DSC   
            I segmentType="MSH" {   //信息头信息
                S mshStr=record
                //消息类型
                S msgType=$P($P(record,"|",9),"^",1)  //ORU,ACK,QRY,QCK,DSR 
                I msgType="ORU" {
                    D SendACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
                }
                I msgType="ORM" {
                }
                I msgType="QRY" {
	                D SendQryACK(mi,record,"AA",0,"Message accepted")
                }
                S resultType=$P(record,"|",11)
            }
        
            I segmentType="PID" {   //患者信息
                
            }
        
            I segmentType="PVI" {   //就诊信息
                
            }
        
            I segmentType="OBR" {   //医嘱信息
                S epis=$P(record,"|",3) 
                S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(record,"|",4)
                S dateStr=$P(record,"|",8)
                I dateStr?14N {
                    S date=$ZDH($E(dateStr,1,4)_"-"_$E(dateStr,5,6)_"-"_$E(dateStr,7,8),3)
                    S time=$ZTH($E(dateStr,9,10)_":"_$E(dateStr,11,12)_":"_$E(dateStr,13,14),1) 
                }
                S code=$P($P(record,"|",5),"^",1)
            }
        
            I segmentType="OBX" {
                S dataTye=$P(record,"|",3)  //NM (numeric) 表示数字值，用于定量项目,
                                            //ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
                S channel=$P(record,"|",4)
                S channel=$P(channel,"^",1)
                S value=$P(record,"|",6)
            
                I $L(channel),dataTye'="ED",dataTye'="IS" {
                    S result=result_channel_par10_value_par11
                }
            }
        
 			//根据条码号获取LIS标本
            I segmentType="QRD" {
                S barcode=$P(record,"|",9)  //QRD|20161208150935|R|D|1|||RD|16120703726|OTH|||T|
                I $L(barcode) {
	                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"MSH")=mshStr
	                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRD")=record
                }
            }
            //根据查询条件获取LIS标本
            I segmentType="QRF" { 
            	S tRecord=record
            	S record=$TR(record," ")
            	S qryStartDate=$P(record,"|",3)
                S qryEndDate=$P(record,"|",4)
                S sampleIdStart=$P(record,"|",5)
                S sampleIdEnd=$P(record,"|",6)
                S:'$L(qryStartDate) qryStartDate=qryEndDate
                S:'$L(qryEndDate) qryEndDate=qryStartDate
                S:'$L(sampleIdStart) sampleIdStart=sampleIdEnd
                S:'$L(sampleIdEnd) sampleIdEnd=sampleIdStart
                //通过样本号段查询  QRF|iFlash3000|||1|9|RCT|COR|ALL|| 
                I sampleIdStart?1.N,sampleIdEnd?1.N {
	                F sampleId=sampleIdStart:1:sampleIdEnd {
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"S",sampleId,"MSH")=mshStr
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"S",sampleId,"QRF")=tRecord
		            }
	            }
	            //通过时间段查询	QRF|iFlash3000|20160122080000|20160122120000|||RCT|COR|ALL||
	            I qryStartDate?1.N,qryEndDate?1.N {
	                F qryDate=qryStartDate:1:qryEndDate {
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate,"MSH")=mshStr
		                S ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate,"QRF")=tRecord
		            }
	            }
            }
        }
    }
  
    //根本样本号获取条码号
    S sampleId=""
    F {
		S sampleId=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",sampleId))
	    Q:'$L(sampleId) 
	    //暂不处理
	}

	//根本日期获取条码号
    S qryDate=""
    F {
		S qryDate=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"D",qryDate))
	    Q:'$L(qryDate) 
	    //暂不处理
	}

	//上传标本
    S barcode="",barcodeIndex=0
    F {
	    S barcode=$O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))
	    Q:'$L(barcode)
	    S mshStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))
	    S barcodeIndex=barcodeIndex+1
	    I $O(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode))="" {
		    S barcodeIndex=""  //最后一个为空
		}
		S mshStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"MSH"))
		S qrdStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRD"))
		S qrfStr=$G(^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi,"B",barcode,"QRF"))
		I '$L(qrdStr) {
			S qrdStr="QRD|"_$TR($ZDT($H,8)," :")_"|R|D|1|||RD||OTH|||T|"
		}
		I '$L(qrfStr) {
			S qrfStr="QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"
		}
		S $P(qrdStr,"|",9)=""
	    S ret=$$SendOrder(mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,barcodeIndex)
	}

	K ^TMPMACHINEEPIS(mi)
    Q
  
 
Save  
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"^"_result,"Test")  
    I $l(epis),$l(result) {
        S QC=""
        ;S result=$$TransResult(mi,result)
        D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
    }
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,resultType)=""
    Q
  
SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
  
SendQryACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="QCK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,"ERR|0|",cr,"QAK|SR|OK|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"QACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"QNAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret
  
ErrHandler
    h 10
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
    Q 
  
    //双向上传医嘱信息,wwh,2015-11-05
SendOrder(mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,DSC)
    N (mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode,DSC)
    S mi=$G(mi),mshStr=$G(mshStr),barcode=$G(barcode),DSC=$G(DSC),qrdStr=$G(qrdStr),qrfStr=$G(qrfStr)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    I '$L(barcode) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码号为空","Upload Error")   
        Q 1 
    }
    I $ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") {             //条码扫描错误
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫描错误,机器未识别","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    } 
    S labno=barcode
    S workGroupMachineDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
    S visiNumberDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
    I '$L(visiNumberDR) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    }
    S visNumberObj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumber).%OpenId(visiNumberDR)
    I '$L(visNumberObj) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    }
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,"Upload Start")
    K ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)
	D ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)
    S result=""
	S chlStr=""
	S chl="",chlCnt=29
	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl))
		Q:'$L(chl)
		S chlStr=chlStr_"DSP|"_chlCnt_"||"_chl_"^^^|||"_cr
		S chlCnt=chlCnt+1
		;S result=result_chl_$C(92)_"?"_$C(44)
	}
 	I '$L(chlStr) {
	 	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的化验项目信息,确定医嘱或项目维护正确?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
	}
	D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,result,"","","")

	S specimenDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(visiNumberDR)),56)
	S specimenName=""
	S:$L(specimenDR) specimenName=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(specimenDR)),3)
	S sampleType="其他"
	I $L(specimenName),",血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,"[(","_specimenName_",") {
		S sampleType=specimenName
	}
	S birdthday=visNumberObj.BirthDate
	S:$L(birdthday)=8 birdthday=birdthday_"000000"
	S:'$L(mshStr) mshStr="MSH|^~\&|YHLO|iFlash3000|||20161208150935||QRY^Q02|18|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"
    S mshSeq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="DSR^Q03"
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
  
    S episode=""
    S workGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6) //##Class(MI.Instrument).GetWorkGroupMachineRowId(mi)
    I $L(workGroupMachineDR) {
    	S OrderNo=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,""))
    	I $L(OrderNo) {
	    	S reportDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,OrderNo,""))
	    	S episode="" //##Class(LIS.Core.Report).GetEpisodeNumber(reportDR)
	    	i $l(reportDR) s Assayno=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(reportDR)),6)
	    }
    }
  
	S order=mshStr_cr //"MSH|^~\&|||||20160122110540||DSR^Q03|14|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"_cr
	S order=order_"MSA|AA|"_mshSeq_"|Message accepted|||0|"_cr
	S order=order_"ERR|0|"_cr
	S order=order_"QAK|SR|OK|"_cr
	S order=order_qrdStr_cr  //"QRD|20160122110540|R|D|1|||RD||OTH|||T|"_cr
	S order=order_qrfStr_cr  //"QRF|iFlash3000|||||RCT|COR|ALL||"_cr
	S order=order_"DSP|1||"_visNumberObj.RegNo_"|||"_cr		//住院号
	S order=order_"DSP|2||"_visNumberObj.BedNo_"|||"_cr		//床号
	S order=order_"DSP|3||"_visNumberObj.SurName_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	/*
	S order=order_"DSP|1||"_visNumberObj.RegNo_"|||"_cr		//住院号
	S order=order_"DSP|2||"_episode_"|||"_cr		//床号
	//S order=order_"DSP|3||"_visNumberObj.SurName_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	S order=order_"DSP|3||"_episode_"|||"_cr	//病人姓名
	*/
	S order=order_"DSP|4||"_birdthday_"|||"_cr				//出生日期
	S order=order_"DSP|5||"_$S(visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=1:"M",visNumberObj.SpeciesDR=2:"F",1:"O")_"|||"_cr	//性别
	S order=order_"DSP|6|||||"_cr				//血型
	S order=order_"DSP|7|||||"_cr				//种族
	S order=order_"DSP|8|||||"_cr				//地址
	S order=order_"DSP|9|||||"_cr				//邮编
	S order=order_"DSP|10|||||"_cr				//家庭电话
	S order=order_"DSP|11|||||"_cr				//样本位
	S order=order_"DSP|12|||||"_cr				//样本采集时间
	S order=order_"DSP|13|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|14|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|15|||||"_cr				//病人类别
	S order=order_"DSP|16|||||"_cr				//医保帐号
	S order=order_"DSP|17|||||"_cr				//收费类型
	S order=order_"DSP|18|||||"_cr				//民族
	S order=order_"DSP|19|||||"_cr				//籍贯
	S order=order_"DSP|20|||||"_cr				//国家
	S order=order_"DSP|21||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本条码
	S order=order_"DSP|22||"_barcode_"|||"_cr	//*样本编号
	S order=order_"DSP|23|||||"_cr				//送检时间
	S order=order_"DSP|24||"_$S(visNumberObj.Urgent=1:"Y",1:"N")_"|||"_cr				//*是否急诊
	S order=order_"DSP|25|||||"_cr				//未用
	S order=order_"DSP|26||"_sampleType_"|||"_cr	//*样本类型(血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,其他)
	S order=order_"DSP|27|||||"_cr	//送检医生
	S order=order_"DSP|28|||||"_cr		//送检科室
	S order=order_chlStr
	S order=order_"DSC|"_DSC_"|"_cr

TransResult(miRowId,result)
	N (miRowId,result)
	S miRowId=$G(miRowId),result=$G(result),newRes=""
	F i=1:1:$L(result,",") {
		S chlStr=$P(result,",",i)
		Continue:'$L(chlStr)
		S chl=$P(chlStr,"\",1)
		S val=$P(chlStr,"\",2)
		Continue:'$L(chl)
		S res=val
		I chl>97,chl<102,val'["?" {
			S res=$$GetQuaResult(miRowId,chl,val)
		}
		S newRes=newRes_chl_$C(92)_res_$C(44)
	}
	Q:$L(newRes) newRes
	Q result

GetQuaResult(miRowId,chl,res)
	N (miRowId,chl,res)
	S miRowId=$G(miRowId),chl=$G(chl),res=$G(res)
	S:res?1"."1.N res="0"_res
	S orgRes=res
	S resPrefix=$E(res,1)
	S:"<>"'[resPrefix resPrefix=""
	I $L(resPrefix) {
		S res=$P(res,resPrefix,2)
	}
	Q:'$L(chl) orgRes
	Q:(res'?0.N1."."1.N)&&(res'?1.N) orgRes
	S tcRefRowId=$O(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexResultChannel",miRowId,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(chl),"")) 
	Q:'$L(tcRefRowId) orgRes
	S tcRowId=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeD(tcRefRowId)),3)
	Q:'$L(tcRowId) orgRes
	S orderNo=$O(^dbo.BTTestCodeRangesI("IndexMaster",tcRowId,""))
	Q:'$L(orderNo) orgRes
	S rangeDR=$O(^dbo.BTTestCodeRangesI("IndexMaster",tcRowId,orderNo,""))
	Q:'$L(rangeDR) orgRes
	S rangeObj=##Class(dbo.BTTestCodeRanges).%OpenId(rangeDR)
	Q:'$L(rangeObj) orgRes

	I res>=rangeObj.ValueHigh {
		I resPrefix="<" {
			Q orgRes
		}
		Q "阳性("_orgRes_")"
	} ELSE {
		I resPrefix=">" {
			Q orgRes
		}
	}
	Q "阴性("_orgRes_")"

MIFCL600OI(mi) 
	///仪器名称:	血细胞分析流水线
	///仪器型号:	迈瑞HL7
	///仪器厂商:	迈瑞
	///通信协议:	HL7
	///交互方式:	双 向
	///接    口:	TCP/IP,RS232
	///备    注:	仪器配置:选择HL7协议,散点图选择:位图   
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
	s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 		//项目分隔符
	s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) 	//结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) 		//抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) 		//药敏结果分隔符
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)  	//端口号
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    Q:$$Start^MI.MIF000(mi)
	s IP=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),9)
	s Port=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)
	s LinkTime=0
	s Device="|TCP|"_Port
	F {
		try{
			;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$ZA,"ZA")
			//未启动客户端/服务端0，客户端断开连接标志20484，无客户端连接20480，有客户端连接28674，连接并建立数据传输28672
			//lis断开
			i $ZA="0" {
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="GB18030"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"lis断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"lisReConnect")
				//throw ##class(%Exception.General).%New("ConnectError","D",,"重新连接失败")
				}
			//仪器断开，或者无数据1min，重启tcp
			i (($ZA="20484")) {
				close par4
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"blockConnect")
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="GB18030"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"重新连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"reConnect")
				s LinkTime=0
				continue
				}
			//连接无数据传输，main每执行6次，即1min，重启tcp
			i $ZA="28674" s LinkTime=$i(LinkTime)
			//正常传输了，就清空计数
			i $ZA="28672" s LinkTime=0
			d Main
	 	}catch ex{
		 s exception="错误:"_ex.Location_"^"_ex.Data_ex.Name
		 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,exception,"读取或写入异常，重启服务端")
	 	}
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
  
Main
	R *R:10
	Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
	Q:$c(R)'=sb   //以sb开头
	S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType,msgType,barcode,mshStr)=""
	S startTime=$P($H,",",2)
	K PLIST
	S index=1
	F {
		S curTime=$P($H,",",2)
		Q:curTime>(startTime+300)  //5分钟内没有处理完则退出循环
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
		R *R:10
		Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出
		I $L($G(PLIST(index)))>=32700 {  //32767
			S index=+$O(PLIST(""),-1)+1
			S PLIST(index)=""
		}
		I $C(R)'=eb,$C(R)'=cr {
			S PLIST(index)=$G(PLIST(index))_$C(R)
		}
		I $C(R)=cr {  	//解析一条记录
			D Record
			K PLIST
			S index=1
		}
		Q:$C(R)=eb   	//循环读取,当为eb的时候则退出
	}
	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,result,"result")
	D Save
	Q

	    		}

			}

			}
		
			I segmentType="OBR" {	//医嘱信息
				S epis=$P(record,"|",2) 
    			S:'$l(epis) epis=$P(record,"|",3)
	     		S code=$P($P(record,"|",5),"^",1)
	     		I code="00003" {	//LJ QCR

			}
		
		
			I segmentType="OBX" {

     										//ST (string) 表示字符串值，用于定性项目
    			S channel=$P(record,"|",4)
    			S channel=$P(channel,"^",1)
    			//s:'$l(channel) channel=$P(record,"|",5)
    			S value=$P(record,"|",5)
    			i value["<" s value=$tr(value,"<")
    			i value[">" s value=$tr(value,">")

	    			S:$l($P(value,"^",2)) result=result_channel_"H"_par10_$P(value,"^",2)_par11
	    			S:$l($P(value,"^",3)) result=result_channel_"I"_par10_$P(value,"^",3)_par11
	    			S value=$P(value,"^",1)
	    		}
    			I dataTye="ST" {
    				S value=$S(value="ò?D?":"阴性",value="??D?":"阳性",1:value)
    			}
    			I $L(channel),dataTye'="ED",dataTye'="IS" {
	    			S result=result_channel_par10_value_par11
    			}
    		
    			I dataTye="IS" {	  
	    			I channel="05001",resultType="Q" {		//质控浓度
		    			S epis=value
		    		}
	    		}
    			S graphTypeDesc=$ZCVT($P($P(record,"|",4),"^",2),"U")
    		
    			I dataTye="ED" {	//图形数据
    				I $ZCVT($P(value,"^",2),"U")=$ZCVT("Image","U") {
	    				S isImage=1  	//位图数据
	    			}
	    			I $ZCVT($P(value,"^",3),"U")=$ZCVT("Octer-stream","U") {
		    			S isBinary=1	//二进制数据(需要绘图)
		    		}
    				S graphType=channel

SendDSP(mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode)
    N (mi,mshStr,qrdStr,qrfStr,barcode)
    S mi=$G(mi),mshStr=$G(mshStr),barcode=$G(barcode),qrdStr=$G(qrdStr),qrfStr=$G(qrfStr)
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"开始上传","Upload") 
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,mshStr,"Upload") 
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,qrdStr,"Upload") 
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,qrfStr,"Upload") 
    b ;a102
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    I '$L(barcode) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码号为空","Upload Error")   
        Q 1 
    }
    I $ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") {             //条码扫描错误
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫描错误,机器未识别","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    } 
    S labno=barcode
    S workGroupMachineDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
    S visiNumberDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
    I '$L(visiNumberDR) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    }
    S visNumberObj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumber).%OpenId(visiNumberDR)
    I '$L(visNumberObj) {
        D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
    }
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,"Upload Start")
    K ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)
	D ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)
    S result=""
	S chlStr=""
	S chl="",chlCnt=0


	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl))
		Q:'$L(chl)
		S chlStr=chlStr_chl_"^"
		S chlCnt=chlCnt+1
		;S result=result_chl_$C(92)_"?"_$C(44)
	}
 	I '$L(chlStr) {
	 	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的化验项目信息,确定医嘱或项目维护正确?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
	}
	i $l(chlStr){
		s chlStr=$e(chlStr,1,*-1)
	}

	/*
	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl))
		Q:'$L(chl)
		S chlStr=chlStr_"DSP|"_chlCnt_"||"_chl_"^^^|||"_cr
		S chlCnt=chlCnt+1
		;S result=result_chl_$C(92)_"?"_$C(44)
	}
 	I '$L(chlStr) {
	 	D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_labno_"对应的化验项目信息,确定医嘱或项目维护正确?","Upload Error")  
        Q 1
	}
	*/
	D Save^MI.MIF000(mi,labno,result,"","","")

	S specimenDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(visiNumberDR)),56)
	S specimenName=""
	S:$L(specimenDR) specimenName=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(specimenDR)),3)
	S sampleType="其他"
	I $L(specimenName),",血清,血浆,尿液,脑脊液,"[(","_specimenName_",") {
		S sampleType=specimenName
	}
	S birdthday=visNumberObj.BirthDate
	S:$L(birdthday)=8 birdthday=birdthday_"000000"
	S:'$L(mshStr) mshStr="MSH|^~\&|YHLO|iFlash3000|||20161208150935||QRY^Q02|18|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"
    S mshSeq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="DSR^Q03"
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
  
    S episode=""
    S workGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6) //##Class(MI.Instrument).GetWorkGroupMachineRowId(mi)
    I $L(workGroupMachineDR) {
    	S OrderNo=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,""))
    	I $L(OrderNo) {
	    	S reportDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",visiNumberDR,workGroupMachineDR,OrderNo,""))
	    	S episode="" //##Class(LIS.Core.Report).GetEpisodeNumber(reportDR)
	    	i $l(reportDR) s Assayno=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(reportDR)),6)
	    }
    }
    s Date=$h
    s datetime=$tr($zd($p(Date,",",1),3),"-","")_""_$tr($zt($p(Date,",",2),1),":","")	//时间
    s JZHWZ=$p(qrdStr,"|",11)		//架子号位置
	S order=mshStr_cr //"MSH|^~\&|||||20160122110540||DSR^Q03|14|P|2.3.1||||||ASCII|||"_cr
	S order=order_"MSA|OK|"_mshSeq_"||||0"_cr

	S order=order_"DSP|1||"_visNumberObj.RegNo_"|"_episode_"|"_visNumberObj.SurName_"|||||||||||||||||||||||||"_cr	
	S order=order_"DSP|2|"_barcode_"|"_barcode_"||N||"_datetime_"||1|"_JZHWZ_"||N||"_datetime_"||||||||"_datetime_"||||||||||||||||||||||||"_cr	
	s order=order_"DSP|3|"_chlCnt_"|"_chlStr_cr


    W sb,order,eb,cr,*-3
    b ;a101
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,sb_order_eb_cr,"H-->M") 
    //$TR($ZDT($H,8)," :") 
    Q 0
  
 
Save

SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
  
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret

SaveHistogram(mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    N (mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    S mi=$G(mi),epis=$G(epis),graphType=$G(graphType),graphOrder=$G(graphOrder),base64Stream=$G(base64Stream)
    Q:'$L(mi) 1
    Q:'$L(epis) 1
    Q:'$L(base64Stream) 1
    Q:'$L(graphType) 1
    S:'$L(graphOrder) graphOrder=0
    S glBinaryStream=##Class(%GlobalBinaryStream).%New()
    While 'base64Stream.AtEnd {
	    S base64=base64Stream.Read()
	    S binary=$system.Encryption.Base64Decode(base64)
	    D glBinaryStream.Write(binary)
	}

	S charStream=##Class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	S maxDot=0
	While 'glBinaryStream.AtEnd {
	    S char=glBinaryStream.Read(1)
	    S ascValue=$ASCII(char)_","
	    S maxDot=maxDot+1
	    D charStream.Write(ascValue)
	}
	D charStream.Write("0")
	K glBinaryStream
	S title=graphType
	S foreColor=12
	S:graphType="PLT" foreColor=10
	S top=10
	S left=10
	S width=300
	S height=150
	S (label,maxValue,memo)=""
    S error=##Class(MI.Instrument).SaveHistogram(charStream,mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,label,title,maxDot,maxValue,memo,foreColor,top,left,width,height)
    I $L(error) {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR(error,"^","--"),"Graph Error")
	}
    K charStream
    Q 0

	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""

		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫描错误,机器未识别","Order")

	///仪器名称:	血细胞分析流水线

	///备    注:	仪器配置:选择HL7协议,散点图选择:位图   
    S mi=$G(mi) 
    Q:'$L(mi)
	s par11=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) 		//项目分隔符
	s par10=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) 	//结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) 		//抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) 		//药敏结果分隔符
	s par4="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)  	//端口号
    S stx=$C(2),etx=$C(3),ack=$C(6),enq=$C(5),eot=$C(4),etb=$C(23)
    S sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)  
    S lf=$C(10),nak=$C(21),(AllRecord,result,epis)="",kk=1
    S (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,errFlag,resultType)=""
    S $ZT="ErrHandler",$EC=""
    Q:$$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi)
	s IP=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),9)
	s Port=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)
	s LinkTime=0
	s Device="|TCP|"_Port
	F {
		try{
			;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$ZA,"ZA")
			//未启动客户端/服务端0，客户端断开连接标志20484，无客户端连接20480，有客户端连接28674，连接并建立数据传输28672
			//lis断开
			i $ZA="0" {
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="GB18030"):20
				use Device
				d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"lis断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"lisReConnect")
				//throw ##class(%Exception.General).%New("ConnectError","D",,"重新连接失败")
				}
			//仪器断开，或者无数据1min，重启tcp
			i (($ZA="20484")) {
				close par4
				;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器断开连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"blockConnect")
				h 2
				open Device:(IP:Port:/IOTABLE="GB18030"):20
				use Device
				;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"重新连接"_$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2)),"reConnect")
				s LinkTime=0
				continue
				}
			//连接无数据传输，main每执行6次，即1min，重启tcp
			i $ZA="28674" s LinkTime=$i(LinkTime)
			//正常传输了，就清空计数
			i $ZA="28672" s LinkTime=0
			d Main
	 	}catch ex{
		 s exception="错误:"_ex.Location_"^"_ex.Data_ex.Name
		 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,exception,"读取或写入异常，重启服务端")
	 	}
		Q:$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
	}
    C par4
    Q
  
Main
	R *R:10
	Q:'$TEST	//如果超时则退出

		}

SendACK(mi,mshStr,ackType="AA",errCode=0,errDesc="Message accepted") //send 'ack' to instrument 
    N (mi,mshStr,ackType,errCode,errDesc)
    S mi=$g(mi),mshStr=$g(mshStr),ackType=$g(ackType),errCode=$g(errCode),errDesc=$g(errDesc)
    S ret=1,sb=$C(11),eb=$C(28),cr=$C(13)
    Q:('$l(mi))||('$l(mshStr)) ret
    S mshStr=$TR(mshStr,cr,"")
    //Q:$l(mshStr,"|")<21 ret
    S ret=0
    S msgRoutine=$P($P(mshStr,"|",9),"^",2)
    S seq=$P(mshStr,"|",10)
    S mshStr=$P(mshStr,"|",1,2)_"|LIS|||"_$P(mshStr,"|",6,$l(mshStr))
  
    S $P(mshStr,"|",9)="ACK^"_msgRoutine
    W sb,mshStr,cr,"MSA|"_ackType_"|"_seq_"|"_errDesc_"|||"_errCode_"|",cr,eb,cr,*-3
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$S(ackType="AA":"ACK",ackType="AE":"Error",ackType="AR":"NAK",1:"NULL"),"H-->M")
    Q ret

SaveHistogram(mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    N (mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,base64Stream)
    S mi=$G(mi),epis=$G(epis),graphType=$G(graphType),graphOrder=$G(graphOrder),base64Stream=$G(base64Stream)
    Q:'$L(mi) 1
    Q:'$L(epis) 1
    Q:'$L(base64Stream) 1
    Q:'$L(graphType) 1
    S:'$L(graphOrder) graphOrder=0
    S glBinaryStream=##Class(%GlobalBinaryStream).%New()
    While 'base64Stream.AtEnd {
	    S base64=base64Stream.Read()
	    S binary=$system.Encryption.Base64Decode(base64)
	    D glBinaryStream.Write(binary)
	}

	S charStream=##Class(%GlobalCharacterStream).%New()
	S maxDot=0
	While 'glBinaryStream.AtEnd {
	    S char=glBinaryStream.Read(1)
	    S ascValue=$ASCII(char)_","
	    S maxDot=maxDot+1
	    D charStream.Write(ascValue)
	}
	D charStream.Write("0")
	K glBinaryStream
	S title=graphType
	S foreColor=12
	S:graphType="PLT" foreColor=10
	S top=10
	S left=10
	S width=300
	S height=150
	S (label,maxValue,memo)=""
    S error=##Class(MI.Instrument).SaveHistogram(charStream,mi,epis,graphType,graphOrder,label,title,maxDot,maxValue,memo,foreColor,top,left,width,height)
    I $L(error) {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR(error,"^","--"),"Graph Error")
	}
    K charStream
    Q 0
  
SendORR(mi,record, AckType="AA",ErrCode=0,ErrDesc="Message accepted",mshStr,epis)
	 N (mi,record,AckType,ErrCode,ErrDesc,mshStr,epis)
	 s mi=$g(mi),record=$g(record),AckType=$g(AckType),ErrCode=$g(ErrCode),ErrDesc=$g(ErrDesc),mshStr=$g(mshStr),epis=$g(epis)

GetPatInfo(labno,mi)
    s labno = $g(labno),mi=$g(mi)
	i $l(labno)=0 q ""
	s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",""_labno,""))
	i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q ""
	//标本信息
	s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
	s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
	i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
	s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
	i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
	s ReceiveDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,66)
	s ReceiveTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,67)
	s ReceiveUserDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,68),ReceiveUser=""
	i $l(ReceiveUserDR) s ReceiveUser=$lg($g(^dbo.SYSUserD(ReceiveUserDR)),3)
	s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
	s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
 	s GivenName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,14)
	i SurName=GivenName s PatName=SurName

SendOrder(mi,mshStr,record)
	N (mi,mshStr,record)
	S mi=$G(mi),mshStr=$G(mshStr),record=$G(record)
	Q:'$L(mi) 1
	Q:'$D(^TMIF(mi)) 1
	S barcode=$P(record,"|",4)
	I '$L(barcode) {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码号为空","Order")
		Q 1
	}
	I $ZCVT(barcode,"U")=$ZCVT("Invalid","U") {				//条码扫描错误
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫描错误,机器未识别","Order")
		Q 1
	} 
	I '$D(^TEPI(barcode)) {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"在检验系统未找到条码:"_barcode_"对应的标本信息,确定条码正确或标本已经接收?","Order")
		Q 1
	}
	K uploadList
	S tsCode="",uploadList=0
	F {
		S tsCode=$O(^TEPI(barcode,1,tsCode))
		Q:'$L(tsCode)
		Q:'$D(^TMIF(mi,0,tsCode))
		S tsDesc=$P($G(^TTAB("TS",tsCode)),"\",1)
		S tsCnt=$O(^TEPI(barcode,1,tsCode,""))
		Q:'$L(tsCnt)
		S status=$P($G(^TEPI(barcode,1,tsCode,tsCnt)),"\",31)
		I status="A" {
			D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫:"_barcode_",医嘱:"_tsCode_"||"_tsDesc_",不是登记状态,不再上传","Order")	
			Continue
		}
		S channel=$$GetTestSetChannel(tsCode)
		I '$L(channel) {
			D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫:"_barcode_",医嘱:"_tsCode_"||"_tsDesc_",未找到通道号","Order")	
			Continue
		}
		Continue:$D(uploadList(tsCode))
		S uploadList(tsCode)=channel
		S uploadList=$I(uploadList)
	}
	I +$G(uploadList)<1 {
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"条码扫:"_barcode_"未找可上传的医嘱","Order")
		Q 1
	}

SEND(str,flag) ; send string to instrument
  i flag=1 d
  .s str=str_etb
  .s chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  e  d
  .s str=str_etx
  .s chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  w stx,str,chsum,cr,lf,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str_chsum,"H-->M")
  f j=1:1:6 r *R:1 i ($c(R)=ack)!($c(R)=eot) q
  i $c(R)=ack d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H<--M") q 0
  i $c(R)=eot d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H<--M") q 0
  i $c(R)=-1 w nak,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,R,"H<--M")
  q 1
CHSUM(x) ; calculate check sum
  n (x) s z=0 f y=1:1:$l(x) s z=z+$a(x,y)
  s z=$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#256\16+1)_$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#16+1)
  q z
ACK  ; send 'ack' to instrument
  w ack,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H-->M")
  q
NEXTTRAY(tray) 
  q tray

/// 			SPLIT:分割符(可以为空)
/// Output：
/// 	非0:返回编码信息:ASC码^汉字^拼音^首拼^四角码^五笔码^区位码^笔划数^郑码
/// 	0：未找到编码信息
/// CreatDate:2011-06-08
/// w ##class(web.DHCINSUPort).GetCNCODE("东华",4,"^")
/// w ##class(web.DHCINSUPort).GetCNCODE("东华",4,"")
GetCNCODE(HANZIS,FLAG, SPLIT)
	s Rtnstr="0"
	q:$g(HANZIS)="" Rtnstr
	s Rtnstr=""
	f i=1:1:$l(HANZIS) d
	.s HANZI=$EXTRACT(HANZIS,i)
	.s ASCIICODE=$ASCII(HANZI)
	.i $D(^DHCCharacterEncoding("0","ASCII",ASCIICODE))'=0 d
	..s rowid=$o(^DHCCharacterEncoding("0","ASCII",ASCIICODE,""))
	..s tmpstr=""
	..s:FLAG="" tmpstr=$g(^DHCCharacterEncoding(rowid))
	..s:FLAG'="" tmpstr=$p(^DHCCharacterEncoding(rowid),"^",FLAG)
	..i Rtnstr=""  d
	...s Rtnstr=tmpstr
	..e  d
	...s Rtnstr=Rtnstr_SPLIT_tmpstr
	.e  d
	..s:Rtnstr="" Rtnstr="?"
	..s Rtnstr=Rtnstr_SPLIT_"?"
	q Rtnstr

ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record, epis, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q
    s (sample,epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
    i '$l(record) q ""
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
  
    i P3'["Import" d Result

Upload
	s AllEpis=""

	..e  s AllEpis=AllEpis_"^"_epis

	i $l(AllEpis) d
	.s ^LISAigel400("Epis",1)=AllEpis

	s ^LISAigel400("OutFlag")=1

    .s rtype=$e(rec,1)
    .i rtype="O" d
    ..s epis=$P($P(rec,"|",3),"^",1)
    .i rtype="R" d
    ..s TestSet=$p($P(rec,"|",3),"^",4)
    ..i TestSet["ABO" d
    ...s allres=$p($P(rec,"|",4),"^",9)
    ...s code1="ABO" s res1=$P(allres,"/",1)_"型"
    ...s code2="Rh" s res2=$p(allres,"/",2)
    ...i res2["+" s res2="阳性"
    ...i res2["-" s res2="阴性"
    ...s result=code1_"\"_res1_","_code2_"\"_res2_","
    ..i TestSet["交叉配血" d
    ...s code1="JCPX" s res1=$p($P(rec,"|",4),"^",3)
    ...i res1="+" s res1="阳性"
    ...i res1="-" s res1="阴性"
    ...s result=code1_"\"_res1_","
    ..i TestSet["不规则抗体筛查" d
    ...s code1="KRQDB" s res1=$p($P(rec,"|",4),"^",3)
    ...i res1["=" d
    ....s res1=$p(res1,"=",2)
    ...i res1="+" s res1="阳性"
    ...i res1="-" s res1="阴性"
    ...s result=code1_"\"_res1_","
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"AllResult<--M")
    i $l(epis),$l(result) d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
    q ""
}

ClassMethod SaveImageMTHD(mi, epis, ImageClass, FileName, FullName, SaveImageRetName, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String

	//通过OtherPara配置取图的在这里通过epis和ImageClass的图片名字提取出流水号和图片类别

    s epis=$g(epis)
    s ImageClass=$g(ImageClass)
    s FileName=$g(FileName)
    s FullName=$g(FullName)
    s SaveImageRetName=$g(SaveImageRetName)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Trace(mi,epis_":"_ImageClass_":"_FileName,"H<--M")
    s (ReceiveDate, ImageOrder, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)=""
    //加上当前时间，防止浏览器缓存
    s FileName=FileName_"?"_$p($h,",",2)
    //OtherPara用^分隔第四位指定SaveImageRetName的话在这里改FileName为新名称。同时让方法返回新图片名字
    s NewFileName=""
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .//图片新名字
    .s NewFileName=epis_"-"_ImageClass_"-"
    .//路径新名字
    .s NewPathName=""
    .s SPLen=$l(FileName,"/")
    .f ii=1:1:SPLen d
    ..i ii<SPLen d
    ...s NewPathName=NewPathName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)_"/"
    ..i ii=SPLen d
    ...s NewFileName=NewFileName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)
    .s NewPathName=NewPathName_NewFileName
    .s FileName=NewPathName
  
    //最后返回NewFileName
    s ret=##Class(MI.Common.MachineResult).SaveImage(ReceiveDate, epis, ImageClass, ImageOrder, FileName, mi, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)
    //返回值控制图片名称模式
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .s ret=NewFileName
    q ret
}

/// Query的执行方法
/// d ##class(%ResultSet).RunQuery("MI.MIFAigel400","QryLabInfo","41","","","","","","","","","","","","","","")
ClassMethod QryLabInfoExecute(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Status
{
    Set repid=$i(^CacheTemp)
    Set ind=1
    s mi=$g(mi),flag=$g(flag)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    s LabnoList=""
    s VisitNumberDR=""
    s AddDate=$tr($zd(+$h,3),"-")
    s DeleteFlag=0
  
    i $d(^LISAigel400("Epis",1)) d
    .s DeleteFlag=1
    .b ;MiUploadDR
    .s labno=$g(^LISAigel400("Epis",1))
    .;s EpisNo=$$getEpis^MI.MIF000(labno,mi)
    .;i '$l(EpisNo) q
    .i '$l(labno) q
    .//测试类型0：文本，1：数据库
    .s TestType="0"
  
    .i TestType="0" d
    ..//文本双向上传开始******************************************************
    ..//控制输出文本的内容
    ..s txtInfo=..GetLabnoInfo(mi,labno)
    ..;s filename="L"_$e($zd($p($h,",",1),8),3,8)_"_"_labno_".txt"
    ..s filename="Servers.dat"
    ..s labno1=$p(labno,"^",1)
    ..s Data=##class(MI.Common.MIFBase).DemoMOutFileInfo(filename,txtInfo,labno1,0,"")
    ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,txtInfo,"上传信息")
    ..d OutputRow
    ..//文本双向上传结束******************************************************
  
    i DeleteFlag=1 k ^LISAigel400("Epis",1)
    Set qHandle=$lb(0,repid,0)
    Quit $$$OK
  
  
OutputRow
    Set ColFields="labno,labnoInfo,patInfo"
    Set ^CacheTemp(repid,ind)=##Class(LIS.Util.Common).TransListNull(Data,ColFields)
    Set ind=ind+1
    quit
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

/// 进制转换，将snum从scale1进制转换为scale2进制
scale(snum, scale1, scale2)
	// 转十进制
	s snum=$g(snum)
	s tnum=0
	s numlong=$l(snum)
	f i=1:1:$L(snum) d
	.s numi=$e(snum,i)
	.s numi=$$Sixteen2Ten(numi)
	.s tnum=tnum+(numi*(scale1**(numlong-i)))

	// 转scale2进制
	s tnum=$g(tnum)
	s num=""
	s GoTo=1
	while (GoTo=1){ 
		s pnum1=tnum
		s tnum=$p(tnum/scale2,".",1)
		s pnum2=pnum1#scale2
		s pnum2=$$Ten2Sixteen(pnum2)
		i tnum<scale2 d
		.s num=tnum_pnum2_num
		.s GoTo=0
		e  s num=pnum2_num
		if (tnum=0)||'$l(tnum) s GoTo=0
	}
	q num

Ten2Sixteen(pnum2)
	i pnum2=10 s pnum2="A"
	i pnum2=11 s pnum2="B"
	i pnum2=12 s pnum2="C"
	i pnum2=13 s pnum2="D"
	i pnum2=14 s pnum2="E"
	i pnum2=15 s pnum2="F"
	q pnum2

Sixteen2Ten(numi)
	i (numi="A")||(numi="a") s numi=10
	i (numi="B")||(numi="b") s numi=11
	i (numi="C")||(numi="c") s numi=12
	i (numi="D")||(numi="d") s numi=13
	i (numi="E")||(numi="e") s numi=14
	i (numi="F")||(numi="f") s numi=15
	q numi

		S ack="{4,1}"		//暂时不处理
		D ACK(mi,ack)
		Q 
	}

	I cmd="5" {	//按测试模式发送结果到LIS
		//{5,[S]A2000,[S]41,[S]132,47925,970200L,183.145F}
		S instrumentId=$P(record,",",2)		//系统标识
		S:instrumentId["[S]" instrumentId=$P(instrumentId,"[S]",2)
		S sampleId=$P(record,",",5)		//测试请求ID
		S sampleNo=$P(record,",",3)		//测试样本编号
		S itemId=$P(record,",",4)		//测试项目编号
		S medicareId="[S]"				//病案号
		//{6,0,47925,[S]41,[S],[S]132}
		S ack="{6,0,"_sampleId_","_sampleNo_","_medicareId_","_itemId_"}"
		D ACK(mi,ack)
		S epis=sampleNo  //sampleId
		S:epis["[S]" epis=$P(epis,"[S]",2)
		// 2017-09-13 WxC 质控标示特殊处理
		;I "H1,L1,P1,C1"[epis S epis="liver1"
		;I "H2,L2,P2,C2"[epis S epis="liver2"
		;I "M1,G1"[epis S epis="HEV1"
		;I "M2,G2"[epis S epis="HEV2"
		//
		S channel=itemId
		S:channel["[S]" channel=$P(channel,"[S]",2)
		S valueL=$P(record,",",6)		//RLU((检测结果相对发光值)
		S valueL=$P(valueL,"L",1)
		S valueF=$P(record,",",7)		//浓度值或S/CO值
		S valueF=$P(valueF,"F",1)
		S:valueF["[S]" valueF=$tr(valueF,"[S]","")
	
		Q:'$L(channel)
		S result=""
		//S result=result_channel_"-L"_$C(par10)_valueL_$C(par11)
		//S result=result_channel_"-F"_$C(par10)_valueF_$C(par11)
		S result=result_channel_ResultDeli_valueF_ItemDeli
		D Save
		Q 
	}

	I cmd="7" {	//按样本模式发送结果到LIS
		//{7,[S]A2000,101,[S]41,3,[S]132,970200L,183.145F,[S]112,673200L,13.15F,[S]113,1378200L,13.5F
		S instrumentId=$P(record,",",2)		//系统标识
		S:instrumentId["[S]" instrumentId=$P(instrumentId,"[S]",2)
		S sampleId=$P(record,",",3)			//样本ID
		S sampleNo=$P(record,",",4)			//测试样本编号
		S itemCount=+$P(record,",",5)		//测试样本包含的测试个数
		S items=$P(record,",",6,$L(record,","))
		S medicareId="[S]"					//病案号 
	
		//{8,0,101,[S]41,[S]
		S ack="{8,0,"_sampleId_","_sampleNo_","_medicareId_"}"
		D ACK(mi,ack)
		S epis=sampleId
		S:epis["[S]" epis=$P(epis,"[S]",2)
		// 2017-09-13 WxC 质控标示特殊处理
		I "H1,L1,P1,C1"[epis S epis="liver1"
		I "H2,L2,P2,C2"[epis S epis="liver2"
		I "M1,G1"[epis S epis="HEV1"
		I "M2,G2"[epis S epis="HEV2"
		//
		S result=""
		F itemIndex=1:3:$L(items,",") {
			S itemId=$P(items,",",itemIndex)	//测试项目编号
			S channel=itemId
			S:channel["[S]" channel=$P(channel,"[S]",2)
			Continue:'$L(channel)
			S valueL=$P(items,",",itemIndex+1)	//RLU((检测结果相对发光值)
			S valueL=$P(valueL,"L",1)
			S valueF=$P(items,",",itemIndex+2)	//浓度值或S/CO值
			S valueF=$P(valueF,"F",1)
			S:valueF["[S]" valueF=$tr(valueF,"[S]","") 
			//S result=result_channel_"-L"_$C(par10)_valueL_$C(par11)
			//S result=result_channel_"-F"_$C(par10)_valueF_$C(par11)
			S result=result_channel_ResultDeli_valueF_ItemDeli
		}
		D Save
		Q  
	}

	I cmd="9" {	//双向  
		//{9,[S]A2000,[S]41}
		S instrumentId=$P(record,",",2)		//系统标识
		S:instrumentId["[S]" instrumentId=$P(instrumentId,"[S]",2)
		S sampleId=$P(record,",",3)			//样本ID
		S epis=sampleId
		S:epis["[S]" epis=$P(epis,"[S]",2)
		///2016-04-13 WXC 扫条码转换仪器
		///D SetTSMachine^MIF000(mi,epis)
  		;s Err=##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).ReceiveLabNoByWGM(mi,epis,"") 
  		;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Err,"核收到仪器返回")
  		s Err=""
  		s RetLL=$$SaveLastMachine^MI.MIF000(mi,epis)
    	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,RetLL,"保存最后仪器")
		K PLIST
		S error=$$BuildItems(mi,epis)
		I $L(error) {
			S ack="{10,1,"_sampleId_"}"
			D ACK(mi,ack)
			d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,error,"Error")
			Q
		}
		S tc="",items=""
		F {
			S tc=$O(PLIST(tc))
			Q:'$L(tc)
			S itemDiluFactor=$G(PLIST(tc))
			S:'$L(itemDiluFactor) itemDiluFactor=1		//稀释倍数,机器内部稀释,必须在该测试项目的支持范围内
			S items=items_"[S]"_tc_","_itemDiluFactor_","
		}
		S items=$E(items,1,$L(items)-1)
		S dilutionFactor=1						//稀释因子

		S ack="{10,0,[S]"_sampleId_","_dilutionFactor_","_isEmergency_","_specimen_","_itemCount_","_items_"}"
		D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ack,"ack<--M")

	d ScanOneNew^MI.MIF000(mi,epis)
	K PLIST
	S tc=""

	Q:'$L(data) ""

// mi:仪器主键

// record:一个数据行合并提交用#enter#分割多行数据

// epis:流水号，前处理提取出了的画

// fileNameOrColName:读文件的是文件全名，数据库的是数据库查询的列名用~分割

// [{"MachID":"#RowID","Type":"Drect","UpTime":"3000","Address":"D:\\Result\\2","UpCDF":"D:\\Result\\1","UpREF":"D:\\Result\\","DealProcess":"MI.MIFXEMSYS","Para":".cdf","PreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealDemoMAll,PreDeal","UPPreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealImage,PreDeal","UpPara":""}]

ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record As %String(MAXLEN=99999999), epis, fileNameOrColName, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    i '$l(record) q ""
    //多行数据
    s recordbak=record
    //返回值
    s retcode=""
    //解析多行合并数据，按#enter#分隔，监听config开启与否合并提交都支持
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
    s (sample,result,date,time,QC,image,retimage,imageR,retimageR,imageres,Ipcode,IpName,conclusion)=""
	f i=1:1:$l(record,"#enter#") d
 	.S resVal=$p(record,"#enter#",i)
 	.//0,2020-12-10,00:00:00,40,XS500,17944,35,[13][10]
 	.//1,RDW-SD,1,41.60,,,,,[13][10]1,WBC,1,4.15,,,,,[13][10]
 	.//3,,HPLT,C:\Laboman4.0\XS500\gram\20201210\0000000040_201210153004_HPLT.gif,1[13][10]
 	.s type=$p(resVal,",",1)
 	.i type=0 s epis=$p(resVal,",",4)
 	.i type=1 d
 	..s code=$p(resVal,",",2),res=$p(resVal,",",4)
 	..s result=result_code_$c(92)_res_$c(44)
 	.i type=3 d
 	..s image=$p(resVal,",",3)
 	..s retimage=$p(resVal,",",4)
 	..s imageR=imageR_image_","
 	..s retimageR=retimageR_retimage_","
 	.i type=4 d   //记录仪器报警信息,Ipcode 信息代码,IpName 信息内容
 	..s Ipcode=$p(resVal,",",3)
 	..s IpName=$p(resVal,",",4)
 	..//s conclusion=conclusion_Ipcode_"^"_IpName
 	..i $l(conclusion) s conclusion=conclusion_"，"_Ipcode_"："_IpName
 	..e  s conclusion=Ipcode_"："_IpName
    .i type=9 d
    ..s imageR=$e(imageR,1,$l(imageR)-1)
    ..s retimageR=$e(retimageR,1,$l(retimageR)-1)
    ..d conversion
    ..s imageres="getimage#"_epis_"#"_imageR_"#"_retimageR
    ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,imageres,"H<--M")
    ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_":"_result,"提示")
    ..i $l(epis),$l(conclusion) d
    ...s epis1=""
    ...i $l(epis)<6 s epis1=$$ChangeEpisnew^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,"")
    ...i $l(epis)>6 s epis1=epis
    ...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis1_":"_conclusion,"报警信息")
    ...i $l(epis1) d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).SaveMajorConclusion(epis1, conclusion, mi)
    ..i $l(conclusion) s result=result_"BJ"_$c(92)_conclusion_$c(44)
    ..i $l(epis),$l(result) d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
    q imageres
  
conversion
	i imageR="HPLT" s imageR="PLT"
	i imageR="HRBC" s imageR="RBC"
	i imageR="HWBC" s imageR="DIFF"
	i imageR="SBASO" s imageR="Baso"
	q
}

/// Creator：      查询患者信息，监听配置上传前处理类后会定时调用这个query查询数据进行上传操作
/// CreatDate：    20140919
/// Description:： 
/// Table：    
/// Input：        mi：仪器主键
/// Output：       仪器信息
/// Return：       仪器信息
/// Others：   
Query QryLabInfo(mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Query(ROWSPEC = "labno,labnoInfo,patInfo")
{
}

/// Query的执行方法
/// d ##class(%ResultSet).RunQuery("MI.MIFXN1000","QryLabInfo","11","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","")
ClassMethod QryLabInfoExecute(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Status
{
        Set repid=$i(^CacheTemp)
    Set ind=1
    s mi=$g(mi),flag=$g(flag)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    s LabnoList=""
    s AddDate="" f  s AddDate=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate)) q:AddDate=""  d
    .s AddTime="" f  s AddTime=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate,AddTime)) q:AddTime=""  d
    ..s MiUploadDR=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,"C",AddDate,AddTime,""))
    ..s labno=$lg(^dbo.RPMachineUploadD(MiUploadDR),3)
    ..i '$l(labno) q
    ..//ref
    ..s labnoInfo=..GetLabnoInfo(mi,labno)
    ..//cdf
    ..s patInfo=..GetPatInfo(mi,labno)
    ..d OutputRow
    Set qHandle=$lb(0,repid,0)
    Quit $$$OK
  
  
OutputRow
    Set Data=$lb(labno,labnoInfo,patInfo)
    Set ColFields="labno,labnoInfo,patInfo"
    Set ^CacheTemp(repid,ind)=##Class(LIS.Util.Common).TransListNull(Data,ColFields)
    Set ind=ind+1
    quit
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" {

/// D ##class(MI.MIFBeckmanRemisol).fileMTHD("38","1,BASO#,1,0.02,,,,,","1")
/// mi:仪器主键
/// record:一个数据行合并提交用#enter#分割多行数据
/// epis:流水号，前处理提取出了的画
/// fileNameOrColName:读文件的是文件全名，数据库的是数据库查询的列名用~分割
/// D ##class(MI.MIFRemisolN).fileMTHD("1","H|\^&|||REMISOL||||||UPLOAD_SIGN=0\INTERPRETATION_FLAG=1\INSTRUMENT_FLAG=1|P|1|20231207134318[13][10]Q|1|^ssss||||||||||O[13][10]L|1[13][10]")
/// D ##class(MI.MIFRemisolN).fileMTHD("24","H|\^&|||Lb1k□V1.5.5||||||UPLOAD_SIGN=1\INTERPRETATION_FLAG=0\INSTRUMENT_FLAG=1|P|1|20241011155213[13][10]P|1||0000000072||彭均秀^||19480902|F|||||||||||||||||普外科门诊[13][10]O|1|24101100017^0020^01|||RO|20241011155213|20241011155213||||||||S|||UV[13][10]R|1|^^^GLU^^2286\2286^1598\1609^^0|7.05^M|||N||R||||20241011102518|AU5800[13][10]R|2|^^^LIPEM^^^^^0|0|||N||R||||20241011102518|AU5800[13][10]R|3|^^^ICTER^^^^^0|0|||N||R||||20241011102518|AU5800[13][10]R|4|^^^HEMOL^^^^^0|0|||N||R||||20241011102518|AU5800[13][10]L|1[13][10]")
ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record As %String(MAXLEN=99999999), epis, fileNameOrColName, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
  
    i '$l(record) q ""
    s (Code,result,date,time,res,QC)=""
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"record")
  
    for i=1:1:$l(record,"[13][10]") d
    .s rec=$p(record,"[13][10]",i)
    .i '$l(rec) q
    .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,rec,"rec")
	.S type=$e(rec,1,1)
	.i type="O" d  q
    ..s epis=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",1)," ")
    .i type="R" d  q
    ..s code=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",4)," ")
    ..S res=$p(rec,"|",4)
    ..s ResNoes=$p(res,"^",2)
    ..s ResNoes=##class(MI.MIFRemisolN).ConvertResNoes(ResNoes) 
    ..s res=$tr($p(res,"^",1)," ","")
    ..s resKZJG=##class(MI.MIFRemisolN).ConvertresKZJG(mi,epis,code,res)
    ..s result=result_code_$c(92)_res_$c(92)_resKZJG_$c(92)_ResNoes_$c(44)
   	.i type="L" d  q
   	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
   	..i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,"","","")
   	q ""
}

/// 获取扩展结果
ClassMethod ConvertresKZJG(mi, epis, code, res)
{
	s code=$g(code),res=$g(res)
	s OutPut=""

	s Labno=$$GetLabnoByEpis(mi,epis)
	i $l(Labno),$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Labno)) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Labno,""))
	.s Age=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR)),18)
	s Age=$g(Age)

	i '$l(code),'$l(res) q OutPut
	i code="BNP",0 d		// BNP N端脑钠肽前体
	.i '$l(Age) q
	.i Age<=50 d
	..i res<=450 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>450,res<=600 s OutPut="急性心衰"
	..i res>600 s OutPut="慢性心衰"
	.i ((Age>50)&&(Age<=75)) d
	..i res<=900 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>900 s OutPut="急性心衰"
	.i Age>75 d
	..i res<=1800 s OutPut="正常"
	..i res>1800 s OutPut="急性心衰"

	i code="25OHD" d		// 25羟维生素D
	.i res<=20 s OutPut="缺乏"
	.i res>20,res<=30 s OutPut="不足"
	.i res>30,res<=100 s OutPut="充足"
	.i res>100 s OutPut="超上限"
	q OutPut

GetLabnoByEpis(mi,Epis)
	s ret=Epis,mi=$g(mi)
	s date=$zd($h,8)
	i '$l(mi) q Epis
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i '$l(WGMachineID) q Epis
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",date,WGMachineID,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Epis))) {
		s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",date,WGMachineID,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Epis),""),-1)
		S VisitNumberDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),2)
		s ret=$lg(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR),2)
		}
	q ret
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

/// 得到标本信息
/// w ##class(MI.MIFRemisolN).GetLabnoInfo(24,"24092600054")
ClassMethod GetLabnoInfo(miRowId, labno) As %String
{
 
	S miRowId=$G(miRowId),labno=$G(labno)
	K PLIST
	Q:'$L(miRowId)||'$L(labno) 0
	 
	K ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$J,miRowId,labno)
	S visitNumberDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	Q:'$L(visitNumberDR) 1
	S visitNumberData=$G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(visitNumberDR))
	Q:'$L(visitNumberData) 2
	D ScanOne^MI.MIF000(miRowId,labno)
   	S chl="",chlList="",hcg5d="",chlCnt=0
   	F {
		S chl=$O(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$J,miRowId,labno,chl))
		i $l(chl)'=0   
		{
		    S:$E(chl,1)="A" chlCnt=chlCnt+1
		    S:chl="A179" hcg5d=chl
		    Continue:chl="A179"
		    S chlList=chlList_"^^^"_chl_"\"
		}  
		else
		{
			Q:'$L(chl)
		}
		 
	}
	 
	I $L(hcg5d) {
		I (chlCnt'=2)&&(chlCnt'=3)&&(chlCnt'=4) {
			S hcg5d="A178"
		}
		S chlList=chlList_"^^^"_hcg5d_"\"
	}
	S chlList=$E(chlList,1,$L(chlList)-1)
	Q:'$L(chlList) 3
	S locationDR=$LG(visitNumberData,22),location=""
	S:$L(locationDR) location=$LG($G(^dbo.BTLocationD(locationDR)),3)
	S doctorDR=$LG(visitNumberData,23),doctor="",doctorCode=""
	I $L(doctorDR) {
		S doctor=$LG($G(^dbo.BTDoctorD(doctorDR)),3)
		S doctorCode=$LG($G(^dbo.BTDoctorD(doctorDR)),2)
	}
	S receiveDate=$LG(visitNumberData,66)
	S receiveTime=$LG(visitNumberData,67)
	S receiveUserDR=$LG(visitNumberData,68),receiveUser=""
	S:$L(receiveUserDR) receiveUser=$LG($G(^dbo.SYSUserD(receiveUserDR)),3)
	S patientId=$LG(visitNumberData,3)
	S surName=$LG(visitNumberData,13)
 	S givenName=$LG(visitNumberData,14)
 	S patName=surName_givenName
	S:surName=givenName patName=surName
	S speciesDR=$LG(visitNumberData,15),species="",speciesCode=""
	I $L(speciesDR) {
		S species=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(speciesDR)),3)
		S speciesCode=$LG($G(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(speciesDR)),2)
	}
	S admTypeDR=$LG(visitNumberData,4),admType=""
	S:$L(admTypeDR) admType=$LG($g(^dbo.BTAdmissionTypeD(admTypeDR)),3)
	S bed=$LG(visitNumberData,27)
	S age=$LG(visitNumberData,18)
	S ageUnitDR=$LG(visitNumberData,19),ageUnit="",ageUnitCode=""
	I $L(ageUnitDR) {
		S ageUnit=$LG($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(ageUnitDR)),3)
		S ageUnitCode=$LG($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(ageUnitDR)),2)
	}
	S collectDate=$LG(visitNumberData,51)
	S collectTime=$LG(visitNumberData,52)
	S collectDateTime=collectDate_##Class(LIS.Core.Util).CvtClientTime(collectTime,"HHMMSS")
	S diagnosis=$LG(visitNumberData,28)
	S birthday=$LG(visitNumberData,16)
	S:"MF"'[speciesCode speciesCode=""
	S:"YMD"'[ageUnitCode ageUnitCode=""
 	S PLIST=0
 	S PLIST($I(PLIST))="H|\^&|||LIS^1|||||REMISOL||P|1|"_$ZD($H,8)_$TR($ZT($P($H,",",2),1),":")
	S patRecord="P|1||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||"
	S $P(patRecord,"|",4)=patientId
	s givenName=""
	S $P(patRecord,"|",6)=surName_"^"_givenName_"^^^"
	S $P(patRecord,"|",8)=birthday_"^"_age_"^"_ageUnitCode
	S $P(patRecord,"|",9)= speciesCode
	S $P(patRecord,"|",14)= doctorCode
	S $P(patRecord,"|",22)= diagnosis  	//诊断
	S $P(patRecord,"|",26)=location
	S PLIST($I(PLIST))=patRecord
	S order="O|1|"_labno_"||"_chlList_"|||||||||||||||||||||"
	S specType=..GetSpecimen(labno)
	//S specTypeId="S"
	// 样品类型，如血清、血浆、尿液等。0-血清，1-血浆，2-尿液，3-脑脊液，4-胃液，5-胸水，6-腹水，7-其他:
	I specType["血清" {
		S specTypeId="0"
	}
	ELSEIF specType["血浆" {
		S specTypeId="1"
	} 
	ELSEIF specType["尿" {
		S specTypeId="2"
	} 
	ELSEIF specType["脑脊液" {
		S specTypeId="3"
	} 
	ELSEIF specType["胃液" {
		S specTypeId="4"
	} 
	ELSEIF specType["胸水" {
		S specTypeId="5"
	} 
	ELSEIF specType["腹水" {
		S specTypeId="6"
	} 
	ELSE {
		S specTypeId="7"
	}
	S $P(order,"|",6)="R"  //priority:R=Routine,S=Stat
	S $P(order,"|",8)=collectDateTime
	S $P(order,"|",12)="A" //Action Code: A=Add,C=Clear,Q=Control
	S $P(order,"|",16)=specTypeId
	S PLIST($I(PLIST))=order
	S PLIST($I(PLIST))="L|1|"
	s del="[13][10]"
	s ret=""
	s seq=""

	f  s seq=$o(PLIST(seq)) q:seq=""  d
	.s ret=ret_PLIST(seq)_del
	Q ret
}

    s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
    s GivenName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,14)

    s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
    s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
    s AgeUnitDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,19),AgeUnit=""
    i $l(AgeUnitDR) s AgeUnit=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(AgeUnitDR)),3)
    s CollectDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,51)
    s CollectTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,52)
    s Diagnose=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,28)
  
    s Sampleda=$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2))
    s Instrument = "XN"
    i $l(mi) s Instrument=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),22)
    s Sampleno=labno   //检测号
    s Sampletype=""
    s Feetype="" ;费别
    s Srcdepno=Location  ;送检科室
    s Srcdocno=Doctor   ;送检医生
    s Userno=ReceiveUser ;检验医生(录入者)
    s Patno=RegNo ;登记号 ""
    s BarCode=""
    s Patna=PatName   ;病人姓名
    s Sex=1  ;性别

    i Species ="女" s Sex="2"
    s Pattype=AdmType   ;病人类型
    s Bedno = BedNo    ;床号
    s Patage=Age  ;年龄
    s Ageunit=""   ;年龄单位
    s Reqno=labno  ;申请号 = 检验号
    s Reqda=""
    i $l(ReceiveDate) s Reqda=$e(ReceiveDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(ReceiveTime,2) ;送检日期 = 接收时间
    s Reportda=""   ;报告日期  = 初审(保存结果)时间
    s Printflag=""  ;打印标志
    s Resultflag=""  ;结果标志
    s Errflag=""  ;错误标志
    s Diagnose = Diagnose   ;诊断
    s Description=""  ;备注
    s Reserve=""  ;保留字段
    s Patnamn=""   ;姓名拼音码
    i $l(CollectDate) s Getda=$e(CollectDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(CollectTime,2) 
    e  s Getda=Reqda ;接收时间/采样日期
    s Wardno=""  ;病区
    s RetString=""
    s RetString=Sampleda_","_Instrument_","_Sampleno_","_Sampletype_","_Feetype_","_Srcdepno_","_Srcdocno_","_Userno_","
    s RetString=RetString_Patno_","_Patna_","_Sex_","_Pattype_","_Bedno_","_Patage_","_Ageunit_","_Reqno_","_Reqda_","
    s RetString=RetString_Reportda_","_Printflag_","_Resultflag_","_Errflag_","_Diagnose_","_Description_","_Reserve_","
    s RetString=RetString_Patnamn_","_Getda_","_Wardno_","_BarCode
    q RetString

ClassMethod TransMachineGroup(mi, epis, machineName)
{
	s ret=""
	i $l(epis)<7 d
	.s epis=$$GetLabnoByEpis(mi,epis)
	s date=$zd($h,8)
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)

	.s ret=##Class(LISSP.DHCRPVisitNumberReport).TransMachineGroup(ParamList,"<Data><P10></P10><P6></P6><P3></P3><P7></P7><P12></P12><P9></P9><P4></P4><P1></P1><P0></P0><P2></P2><P14></P14><P11></P11><P13></P13><P8></P8><P5></P5></Data>","8280^18^0^2^1","")

	s mi=$g(mi) 
	i '$l(mi) q
	s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,11)=mi
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  //端口号
	S $ECODE=""  //捕获运行时错误,并显示
	//控制字符
	S stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4)
	S lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),(result,epis)="",etb=$c(23)
	s isDebug=1,iError=0
	s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,10)=mi
	i $$StartUTF8^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	s ^TMPMACH10(mi,50)=$h
  	c Port
  	q
 
Main 
  ;s ^MIFSIMENSTRecive=$zdt($h,3)
  S $ZT="RuntimeError"
  r *R:10 e  d  q
  .;d BUILD2
  i $c(R)'=enq Q
  s AllRecord=""
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H<--M")
  d ACK
  f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  d
  .i $c(R)'=stx q
  .s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,"",lf) q:'$l(record)
  .s record=$e(record,2,$l(record)-1)
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
  .i $l(record,etb)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,1,$l(record)-1),etb,1)
  .i $l(record,etx)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,1,$l(record)-1),etx,1)  
  .d ACK
  .s type=$tr($p(record,"|",1)," ")
  .i type="M" d  q
  ..s Intype=$tr($p($p(record,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
  ..s Inlabno=$tr($p($p(record,"|",4),"^",2)," ")
  ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Inlabno,"Inlabno")
  ..try{s ret=##class(MI.Special.AutomaticReceipt).ZDHS(mi,Inlabno)}catch{}		//YHR 20230910 生化流水线自动核收
  
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=eot:"EOT",1:R),"H<--M")
  s k=1
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,AllRecord,"AllRecord")
  i $c(R)=eot,$l(AllRecord) d
  .s (mid,sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC,flag,machiecode)=""
  .f i=1:1:$l(AllRecord,cr) d
  ..s rec=$p(AllRecord,cr,i)
  ..s type=$tr($p(rec,"|")," ")
  ..i type="H" d  q
  ..i type="M" d  q
  ...s Intype=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
  ...s Inlabno=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",4),"^",2)," ")
  ...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Inlabno,"Inlabno")
  ...;try{s ret=##class(MI.Special.AutomaticReceipt).ZDHS(mi,Inlabno)}catch{}		//YHR 20230910 生化流水线自动核收
  ..i type="O" d  q
  ...s epis=$tr($p(rec,"|",3)," ")
  ..i type="R" d  q
  ...s code=$p($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",4),"/",1)
  ...s flag=$p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",8)
  ...s machiecode=$p($p(rec,"|",14),"_",1)
  ...i machiecode="CentaurXP",flag'="DOSE" Q
  ...//R|1|^^^Glu^Neat^1.0^^^N|7.70|||||||^batch|20191116093550||Advia2400_1【13】【3】C2
  ...s MachID=$P($p(rec,"|",14),$C(13),1)
  ...s res=$p(rec,"|",4)
  ...I res="No Result" s res=""
  ...i '$l(code) q
  ...i '$l(res) q
  ...s result=result_code_ResultDeli_res_ItemDeli
  ...s DateStr=$p(rec,"|",13)
  ...s:'$L(DateStr) DateStr=$p(rec,"|",12)
  ...i $l(DateStr) d
  ....s date=$zdh($e(DateStr,1,4)_"-"_$e(DateStr,5,6)_"-"_$e(DateStr,7,8),3)
  ....s time=($e(DateStr,9,10)*3600)+($e(DateStr,11,12)*60+$e(DateStr,13,14))
  ..s k=k+1
  ..i type="L" d Last q 
  q
  
Last
	;s resultmi=40
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,mi,"仪器rowid")
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,date_"^"_time_"^"_epis_"^:"_result,"Save in SIMENS")
	i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
	s (epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
    ///标本核收
   ; i $l(epis),'$d(^DHCUploadAllBAK("B",epis)) s retVal=$$ReceiveLabno^MI.MIF000(28,epis,"")
	q

RuntimeError
	h 10
    s iError=iError+1
    d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"Error Code:"_$ECODE_",Error:"_$ZERROR,"Runtime Error")
    i iError>100  s ret=$$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi)
    Q
        
     ///CreateDate：  20140717
	///Description： 构建医嘱列表
	///Table DHC_LoadSpecimen
	///Input：		
	///Output：	
	///Return：		
	///Others：DHCLoadSpecimen(0,"DateTime","TDMTS","C",62301,42467,"T623010010","T101",1)
	/// ^DHCLoadSpecimen({DHC_LoadSpecimen.DLSP_LabNo},{DHC_LoadSpecimen.DLSP_TS},{DHC_LoadSpecimen.DLSP_TSCNT},"TC",{DLST_TestCode}) 
    /// ^DHCLoadSpecimen({DLSP_LabNo},{DLSP_TS},{DLSP_TSCNT})
    ///   W $$BUILD2^DEBUG
BUILD2
	i $d(^DHCENQ(1)) d
	.d SendENQ
	.k ^DHCENQ
	Q  //wwh,20140812,不上传标本
	K ^TMP($zn,$j)
	I '$D(^DHCLoadSpecimen(0,"DateTime",mi,"C",+$h)) H 10 Q
	S SIMTT="" F  S SIMTT=$o(^DHCLoadSpecimen(0,"DateTime",mi,"C",+$h,SIMTT)) Q:SIMTT=""  D
	.S SIMEpis="" F  S SIMEpis=$o(^DHCLoadSpecimen(0,"DateTime",mi,"C",+$h,SIMTT,SIMEpis)) Q:SIMEpis=""  D
	..S SIMTS="" F  S SIMTS=$O(^DHCLoadSpecimen(0,"DateTime",mi,"C",+$h,SIMTT,SIMEpis,SIMTS)) Q:SIMTS=""  D
	...S epis=SIMEpis
	...S SIMAck=$$BUILD()
	...;;;I (SIMAck=3)!(SIMAck=6) D  
	...I SIMAck=0 D  
	....;;S err=$$UpdSendStatus^DHCLABLoadSpecimen(mi,epis,1,SIMTS)
	....S err=$$UpdSendStatus^DHCLABLoadSpecimen(mi,epis,1)
	...E  D
	....S err=$$UpdSendStatus^DHCLABLoadSpecimen(mi,epis,0)
	Q 
 
BUILD() 
	S episx=epis,epis=$P(epis,"-",1),suffix="",RetAck=1
	S ^TMPsim(1)=epis
	I $l(epis),'$D(^TEPI(epis,1)) S suffix=$E(epis,$L(epis)),epis=$E(epis,1,$L(epis)-1) I $L(epis),'$D(^TEPI(epis,1)) Q
	S ^TMPsim(2)=epis_","_mi_","_suffix

	;;;S err=$$CreateTCList^MIF000(mi,epis,SIMTS)  ;创建上传医嘱列表
	S err=$$CreateTCList^MIF000(mi,epis)  ;创建上传医嘱列表
	M ^TMPCHL(7)=^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",$j)
	Q:'$D(^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",$j,mi,epis_suffix))
	M ^TMPCHL(2)=^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",$j)
	S (surn,givn,sex,dob,date,urno,age,loc)=""
 
	; check for entered/pre-entered patient details
	K PLIST I '$$select^LVBEPVIS(epis,"Y") D
	.F j="surn;3","givn;4","sex;5","dob;6","date;12","urno;20","age;26","loc;66" S @($P(j,";"))=$g(PLIST($p(j,";",2)))
	K PLIST S sex=$P(sex,$c(1),1) s:sex="" sex="M"
	S urno=$p(urno,$c(1),1)
	I givn=surn s givn=""
	S diag=$P($G(^TEPI(epis,8)),"\",15) ;;; 诊断
	S SpecType=$$GetSpecType(epis)  ;;; 标本
	I $l(epis),$D(^TEPI(epis)) D
	.D scanone^MIF000(mi,epis)  ;^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",208912,"AH7471","A611071030",1)=
	.S tcx=""
	.S chl="" F  S chl=$o(^TMP("MIF-SINGLE",$j,mi,epis,chl)) Q:chl=""  D
	..;s tcs=tcs_"^^^"_chl_"/\"
	..S tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"^0\"
	.S tcx=$e(tcx,1,$L(tcx)-1)
	.I '$L(tcx) S tcx="^^^^^^0"
	.S xx=$$extdate2^SSUTIL4($h),date=$p(xx,"/",3)_$p(xx,"/",2)_$p(xx,"/",1)
	.S xx=$$exttime^SSUTIL4($p($h,",",2)),time=$p(xx,":",1)_$p(xx,":",2)_"00"
	.S temepis=""
	.;1H|\^&|||BSLIS^V3.00|||||||P|1<CR>
	.S str="1H|\^&|||BSLIS^V3.00|||||host|TSDWN^REPLY|P|1"_cr   ;头信息
	.;2P|1|0010332409|0010332409||Doe^JohnlSmith||19150826|F|||||||||||||||||5500|||||||||<CR>
	.S str=str_"2P|1"_cr  ;病人信息
	.S str=str_"2P|1"_cr 
	.I epis="N" s epis=""
	.;3O|1|112448100||^^^TP^^^0\^^^ALB^^^0|R||20110826112206||||A|hep|lipemic||Serum||||||||||Q<CR>
	.S str=str_"3O|1|"_epis_"||"_tcx_"|R||"_date_time_"||||A|hep|lipemic||"_SpecType_"||||||||||"
	.S str=str_"Q"_cr
    .;4L|1<CR>
	.S str=str_"4L|1|"_cr
	.S RetAck=$$Send(epis,str) 
	.K ^TMIF("MIF_SINGLE",$j,mi,epis)
	S ^TMPsim(mi,$H,epis)=str_"||"_RetAck
	Q RetAck 

Send(epis,str)  ; send list of orders if exists
  W enq,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H-->M")
  S ret=1
  F j=1:1:10 R *R:1 I $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq)  Q 
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"1H<--M")
  I $c(R)=enq Q ret
  I $c(R)'=ack W eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H-->M") Q ret
  I $L(str)>241 D
  .S str1=$e(str,1,241)
  .S ret=$$SEND(str1,1)
  .S str2="2"_$E(str,242,$L(str))
  .S ret=$$SEND(str2,0)
  E  D
  .S ret=$$SEND(str,0)
  ;f j=1:1:10 r *R:1 i $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq) q
  ;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"2H<--M")
  W eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H-->M")
  Q ret

 
SEND(str,flag)  ; send string to instrument
  I flag=1 D
  .S str=str_etb
  .S chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  E  D
  .S str=str_etx
  .S chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  W stx,str,chsum,cr,lf,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str_chsum,"H-->M")
  F j=1:1:6 R *R:1 I ($c(R)=ack)!($c(R)=eot) Q
  I $c(R)=ack d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H<--M") Q 0
  I $c(R)=eot d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H<--M") Q 0
  I $c(R)=-1 W nak,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,R,"H<--M")
  Q 1
  
CHSUM(x)  ; calculate check sum
  n (x) s z=0 f y=1:1:$l(x) s z=z+$a(x,y)
  s z=$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#256\16+1)_$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#16+1)
  q z
  
ACK  ; send 'ack' to instrument
  w ack,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H-->M")
  q
NEXTTRAY(tray)  
  q tray

  s labno=$g(labno)
  s spdr=$o(^TEPI(labno,4,""))

  i $l(spdr),$d(^TTAB("SPEC",spdr)) s spec=$p(^TTAB("SPEC",spdr),"\",1)
  i spec["血" s RetVal="SE"
  i spec["尿" s RetVal="UR"
  q RetVal

  F j=1:1:10 R *R:1 I $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq) d
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"1H<--M")
  I $c(R)=enq Q 
  I $c(R)'=ack W eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"EOT","H-->M")
  q

MIFNYSIMSend(mi)  ; 7/17/14 ; ASTM protocol  - 西门子流水线(MCR)
	s mi=$g(mi) 
	i '$l(mi) q
	s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,11)=mi
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),10)  //端口号
	//控制字符
	s isDebug=1,iError=100
	S stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4)
	S lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),(result,epis)="",etb=$c(23)
	s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,10)=mi
	i $$Start^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
	s ^TMPMACH10(mi,50)=$h
  	c Port
  	q
  
Main
  S $ZT="RuntimeError",$ECODE=""  //捕获运行时错误,并显示
  r *R:10 e  d  q
  .D BUILD2
  i $c(R)=enq d
  .s AllRecord=""
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ENQ","H<--M")
  .d ACK
  .f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  d
  ..i $c(R)'=stx q
  ..s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,"",lf) q:'$l(record)
  ..s record=$e(record,2,$l(record)-1)
  ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
  ..i $l(record,etb)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,1,$l(record)-1),etb,1)
  ..i $l(record,etx)>1 s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p($e(record,1,$l(record)-1),etx,1)  
  ..;s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p(record,etb,1)
  ..;s AllRecord=AllRecord_$p(record,etx,1)
  ..d ACK
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(R)=eot:"EOT",1:R),"H<--M")
  .i $c(R)=eot,$l(AllRecord) d
  ..s (mid,sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC)=""
  ..f i=1:1:$l(AllRecord,cr) d
  ...s rec=$p(AllRecord,cr,i)
  ...s type=$tr($p(rec,"|")," ")
  ...i type="H" d  q
  ...i type="M" d  q
  ....s Intype=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
  ....s Inlabno=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",4),"^",2)," ")
  ....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Inlabno,"Inlabno")
  ....try{s ret=##class(MI.Special.AutomaticReceipt).ZDHS(mi,Inlabno)}catch{}		//YHR 20230910 生化流水线自动核收
  
  ....i Intype="I" d
  .....i $l(Inlabno)=0 q
  .....q:'$d(^TEPI(Inlabno))
  .....s temts="" f  s temts=$o(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts)) q:temts=""  d
  ......;q:'$d(^TMIF(mi,0,temts))
  ......s temtscnt="" f  s temtscnt=$o(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt)) q:temtscnt=""  d
  .......s:$P(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt),"\",27)="" $P(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt),"\",27)=mi
  .......s:$P(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt),"\",36)="" $P(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt),"\",36)=$P(^TEPI(Inlabno,1,temts,temtscnt),"\",60) 
  ...i type="O" d  q
  ....s epis=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",1)," ")
  ....s qcid=$tr($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",2)," ")
  ....s qcid=$tr(qcid,"-")
  ....s QCStat=$tr($p(rec,"|",4)," ")  
  ....s SpecStat=$tr($p(rec,"|",6)," ")
  ....i SpecStat="S" s epis="E"_epis
  ....i QCStat="Q" s QC="\"_qcid,epis=qcid
  ....s datex=$p(rec,"|",23)
  ....s date=$e(datex,5,6)_"/"_$e(datex,7,8)_"/"_$e(datex,1,4),date=$$intdate^SSUTIL4(date)
  ....s time1=$e(datex,9,10)_":"_$e(datex,11,12)_":"_$e(datex,13,14),time1=$$inttime^SSUTIL4(time1)
  ...i type="R" d  q
  ....s code=$p($p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",4),"/",1)
  ....s flag=$p($p(rec,"|",3),"^",8)
  ....s mid1=$p(rec,"|",14)
  ....i mid1'="" s mid=mid1
  ....s res=$p(rec,"|",4)
  ....s ^Test(i)=res_"\"_flag
  ....i mid1["CentaurXP",$l(code),$l(res) D
  .....i flag="DOSE" d
  ......s result=result_code_$c(par10)_res_$c(par11)
  //....E  D
  ....i $l(code),$l(res) D
  .....s result=result_code_$c(par10)_res_$c(par11)
  ...  //i type="L" d Last q
  D BUILD2
  q
  
Last	; file result if exist
	s AllRecord=""
	i time1="" s time1=$p($h,",",2)
	s time=time1
	S date=$P($H,",",1),time=$P($H,",",2)
	i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
	q

RuntimeError

/// w ##class(MI.MIFDL96A2).RExpertRules("sadsa*da*dasds*sad ")
/// 20240802    格式化专家规则
ClassMethod RExpertRules(expertRules As %String) As %String
{
    s expertRules=$g(expertRules)
    i expertRules["*" d
    .s expertRules="1、"_expertRules
    .f i=2:1:$l(expertRules,"*") d
    ..s expertRules=$p(expertRules,"*",1)_" "_i_"、"_$p(expertRules,"*",2,*)
    q expertRules

/// 保存专家规则
/// 20240704 
/// w ##class(MI.MIFDL96A2).SaveZJGZ("6633","40",1,"多黏菌素B应与一种或多种活性抗生素联合使用，建议咨询感染诊治专家。*头孢噻肟的折点基于1g□q8h的给药方案。*亚胺培南的折点基于500mg□q6h或1g□q8h的给药方案。*美罗培南的折点基于1g□q8h的给药方案。*头孢唑啉的结果可预报非复杂性的泌尿系统感染的大肠埃希菌对口服头孢拉定、头孢地尼、头孢克罗、头孢丙烯、头孢泊肟、头孢呋辛的敏感性。*头孢西丁的折点基于至少8g□qd的给药方案。*仅肠沙门菌伤寒血清型和志贺菌属具有阿奇霉素的临床推荐折点。*氨苄西林的结果可用于预报阿莫西林的敏感性。*环丙沙星折点基于静脉注射400mg□q12h或口服500mg□q12h给药方案。*头孢吡肟的敏感折点基于1g□q12h的给药方案。*头孢呋辛（注射）的折点基于1.5g□q8h的给药方案。*治疗非复杂泌尿道感染的头孢唑林折点是基于1g□q12h的给药方案。*治疗非复杂泌尿道以外感染的头孢唑林折点是基于2g□q8h的给药方案。*多黏菌素B应给予负荷剂量和最大推荐剂量。*厄他培南的折点基于1g□qd的给药方案。*对于肺炎即使黏菌素或多黏菌素B全身给药，亦很可能无效。")
ClassMethod SaveZJGZ(epis, mi, isolate, ExpertRules)
{
	s ^GYN("Rule",epis)=$lb(epis, mi, isolate, ExpertRules)
   //TestCodeDR 细菌一，细菌二，细菌三 570,586,575
	s epis=$g(epis),mi=$g(mi),ExpertRules=$g(ExpertRules)
	s TestCodeDR=""
	i isolate=1 s TestCodeDR=261
	i '$l(mi) q 0
	i '$l(epis) d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"流水号不能为空","保存检测结论返回")  q 0
	//报告可能核收到微生物培养的四个小组
	s WGM=""
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",15," "_epis)) s WGM=15
	i '$l(WGM) q 0

	s sc=0
	s transmitDate="" f  s transmitDate=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGM," "_epis,transmitDate)) q:transmitDate=""  d
	.s ReportDR="" f  s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGM," "_epis,transmitDate,ReportDR)) q:ReportDR=""  d 
	..//IndexReportItem On (VisitNumberReportDR, TestCodeDR)
	..i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResultI("IndexReportItem",ReportDR,TestCodeDR)) q
	..s ResultDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResultI("IndexReportItem",ReportDR,TestCodeDR,""))
	..s objRep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResult).%OpenId(ResultDR)
	..s EXPRlues=objRep.ExpertRule
	..i EXPRlues=ExpertRules q  //专家规则不再变化，不存
	..s objRep.ExpertRule=ExpertRules
	..s sc=objRep.%Save()
	..i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"保存检测结论失败","保存检测结论失败返回") q
	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ExpertRules,"保存检测结论成功返回")
	q sc
}

/// D ##class(MI.MIFLISMonitorTest)SaveImageMTHD("7","9999", "","175")
/// mi:仪器
/// epis：流水号，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片名称，自己在保存前提取流水
/// ImageClass:图片类别，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片名称，自己在保存前提取图片类型
/// FileName:保存在文件服务的相对路径，默认不动
/// FullName:文件全路径，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片全路径名称，满足有的图片名称无法得到流水和图片类别的情况
ClassMethod SaveImageMTHD(mi, epis, ImageClass, FileName, FullName, SaveImageRetName, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	//通过OtherPara配置取图的在这里通过epis和ImageClass的图片名字提取出流水号和图片类别
    s mi=$g(mi)
    s epis=$g(epis)
    s ImageClass=$g(ImageClass)
    s FileName=$g(FileName)
    s FullName=$g(FullName)
    s SaveImageRetName=$g(SaveImageRetName)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Trace(mi,epis_":"_ImageClass_":"_FileName,"H<--M")
    s (ReceiveDate, ImageOrder, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)=""
    //加上当前时间，防止浏览器缓存
    s FileName=FileName_"?"_$p($h,",",2)
    //OtherPara用^分隔第四位指定SaveImageRetName的话在这里改FileName为新名称。同时让方法返回新图片名字
    s NewFileName=""
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .//图片新名字
    .;s NewFileName=epis_"-"_ImageClass_"-"
    .//路径新名字
    .s NewPathName=""
    .s SPLen=$l(FileName,"/")
    .f ii=1:1:SPLen d
    ..i ii<SPLen d
    ...s NewPathName=NewPathName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)_"/"
    ..i ii=SPLen d
    ...s NewFileName=NewFileName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)
    .s NewPathName=NewPathName_NewFileName
    .s FileName=NewPathName
  
    //最后返回NewFileName
    s ret=##Class(MI.Common.MachineResult).SaveImage(ReceiveDate, epis, ImageClass, ImageOrder, FileName, mi, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)
    //返回值控制图片名称模式
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .s ret=NewFileName
    q ret
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }

    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

/// Description：  保存报警提示信息
/// Input：        mi 仪器主键,epis 流水号,expertRules 报警信息,expertRulesType 报警信息仪器类型(存在值将报警信息进行转换，不存在则直接保存报警信息)
/// 			   SaveTypeData (分隔符^)保存类型(1:次评价不打印，2:主评价可打印)，为空默认为1
/// 				   			是否保存未转换数据(1:保存，0:不保存)，为空默认为0
/// Output：   
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(57,1200150259127,"CSCSCS") 
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(2,1892,"Basophilia：嗜碱性粒细胞增加；NRBC?：有核红细胞？；Anisocytosis：红细胞大小不均；Macrocytosis：大红细胞症；Hypochromia：低色素性；WBC_Abn_Scattergram：白细胞异常散点图；IG_Present：幼稚粒细胞存在；PLT_Abn_Distribution：血小板异常直方图；Blasts/Abn_Lympho?：原始细胞/异常淋巴细胞?") 
/// DeBug:		   w ##Class(MI.Special.Common).SaveAlarmInformation(9,63,"13003","DMD7") 
ClassMethod SaveAlarmInformation(mi, epis, expertRules, expertRulesType, SaveTypeData)
{
	s mi=$g(mi)
    s epis=$g(epis)
    s expertRules=$g(expertRules)
    s SaveTypeData=$g(SaveTypeData)
    s SaveType=$p(SaveTypeData,"^",1)
    i '$l(SaveType) s SaveType=1		// 保存类型(1:次评价不打印，2:主评价可打印)，为空默认为1
    s expertRulesIsSave=$p(SaveTypeData,"^",2)
    i '$l(expertRulesIsSave) s expertRulesIsSave="0"	// 是否保存未转换数据(1:保存，0:不保存)，为空默认为0
    s expertRulesType=$g(expertRulesType)
  
    // 配置信息
    s Sep="；"	// 文本串分隔符
  
    // 转换报警信息
    i $l(expertRulesType) d
    .s InputInfo=""
    .s PoliceInfo=expertRules
    .i $l(PoliceInfo),$d(^LISPolice(expertRulesType,PoliceInfo)) d
  	..s InputInfo=$g(^LISPolice(expertRulesType,PoliceInfo))
  	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,PoliceInfo_"$$"_InputInfo,"报警信息")
  	.i $l(InputInfo) d
  	..s expertRules=InputInfo
  	.e  d
  	..i expertRulesIsSave=0 d
  	...s expertRules=""
  	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"转换报警信息失败。","报警信息异常")
  	..e  d
  	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"保存原始报警信息。","报警信息异常")
  	i '$l(expertRules) q ""
  
    s ReportDR=$$GetReportID(mi,epis)
    i '$l(ReportDR) q ""
    s obj=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
    s TMPstr=obj.MinorConclusion
    i TMPstr'[expertRules d
    .i $l(TMPstr) d
    ..s Str=TMPstr_Sep_expertRules
    .e  d
    ..s Str=expertRules
    .s Str=$$DislodgeRepetition(Str,Sep)
    .i SaveType=1 d
    ..s obj.MinorConclusion=Str		//YHR 20230411 保存在报告次评价 不可打印
    .i SaveType=2 d
    ..s obj.MinorConclusion=Str		//YHR 20230411 保存在报告主评价 可打印
    s ret=obj.%Save()
    D Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ret_"$$"_expertRules,"SaveAlarmInformation")
    q ret
  
GetReportID(mi,AssayNo)
	// 根据仪器试验号获取报告ID
	s mi=$g(mi),AssayNo=$g(AssayNo)
	s ReportDR=""
	i '$l(AssayNo) q ReportDR
	s WGMachineID=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),6)
	i $D(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGMachineID,AssayNo)) d
	.s TransmitDate=$zd($p($h,",",1),8)
	.s ReportDR=$O(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGMachineID,AssayNo,TransmitDate,""),-1)
	i $l(ReportDR) q ReportDR
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",AssayNo)) d
	.s VisitnumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",AssayNo,""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1)) d
	..s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1,""),-1)
	q ReportDR

DislodgeRepetition(Str,Sep)
	// 去除重复信息
	s Sep=$g(Sep)
	i '$l(Sep) s Sep="；"
	k ^LISTMPStr
	s ret=""
	f p=1:1:$l(Str,Sep) d
	.s Strp=$p(Str,Sep,p)
	.i '$l(Strp) q
	.s ^LISTMPStr("Data",Strp)=""
	s GStr="" f  s GStr=$o(^LISTMPStr("Data",GStr)) q:GStr=""  d
	.s ret=ret_Sep_GStr
	s ret=$e(ret,2,*)
	k ^LISTMPStr
	q ret
}

/// 万泰获取报警信息，将字符串转换为16进制后，从后往前根据位数为1获取第几位报警信息
/// w ##class(MI.Special.JudgeResult).GetPolice("42000100000")
ClassMethod GetPolice(PoliceInfo)
{
	s str=##class(MI.Special.ScaleConversion).scaleconversion(PoliceInfo,"16","2")
	k ^LISCaris200("Data")
	s strLong=$l(str)
	f i=1:1:strLong d
	.s stri=$e(str,i)
	.i stri=1 d
	..s ^LISCaris200("Data",strLong+1-i)=1
	q ""
}

/// w ##class(MI.Special.ScaleConversion).scaleconversion4("42000100000","16","2")
/// 进制转换
ClassMethod scaleconversion(snum, scale1, scale2)
{
	s cnum=..Sixteen2Ten(snum,scale1)
	s num=..Ten2Other(cnum,scale2)
	q num
}

/// w ##class(MI.Special.ScaleConversion).scaleconversion2()
/// 十六进制转十进制
ClassMethod Sixteen2Ten(snum, scale)
{
	s snum=$g(snum)
	s tnum=0
	s numlong=$l(snum)
	f i=1:1:$L(snum) d
	.s numi=$e(snum,i)
	.s numi=$$Sixteen(numi)
	.s tnum=tnum+(numi*(scale**(numlong-i)))
	q tnum
Sixteen(numi)
	i (numi="A")||(numi="a") s numi=10
	i (numi="B")||(numi="b") s numi=11
	i (numi="C")||(numi="c") s numi=12
	i (numi="D")||(numi="d") s numi=13
	i (numi="E")||(numi="e") s numi=14
	i (numi="F")||(numi="f") s numi=15
	q numi
}

/// w ##class(MI.Special.ScaleConversion).scaleconversion3(4535486513152,2)
/// 十进制转其他进制
ClassMethod Ten2Other(snum, scale)
{
	s snum=$g(snum)
	s tnum=""
	s GoTo=1
	while (GoTo=1){ 

		s pnum1=snum
		s snum=$p(snum/scale,".",1)
		s pnum2=pnum1#scale
		s pnum2=$$Sixteen(pnum2)
		i snum<scale d
		.s tnum=snum_pnum2_tnum
		.s GoTo=0
		e  s tnum=pnum2_tnum

		if (snum=0)||'$l(snum) s GoTo=0
	}
	q tnum

Sixteen(pnum2)
	i pnum2=10 s pnum2="A"
	i pnum2=11 s pnum2="B"
	i pnum2=12 s pnum2="C"
	i pnum2=13 s pnum2="D"
	i pnum2=14 s pnum2="E"
	i pnum2=15 s pnum2="F"
	q pnum2
}
